external_knowledge:
- 'Technology companies' refers to companies belonging to the 'Technology' category or its sub-categories; 
- 'Accessed company metrics' refers to views or downloads of performance metrics by users mapped to these companies; 
- 'Access summaries' include total count, first date, last date, role-based access count, download count, and view count.

sql:
SELECT SUM(CAST(REPLACE(pm.views, ',', '') AS INTEGER)) AS total_views
FROM performance_metrics pm
WHERE pm.view_period BETWEEN date('now', '-1 month') AND date('now');
